        }
      ]
}



When a second attempt is processed, the retryAttempt__c is incremented by 1 to be set at 2.

Then 3 and 4 ; once it’s 4, the query won’t retrieve it in the next execution, the middleware action is ignored and needs to be analyzed by IT.

